PYTHON COMPATIBILITY
--------------------

This project is compatible with both python-2.7 and python-3.

UNIT TESTS EXECUTION
--------------------

By being in specific directory:

> cd [location of multicast_chat]
> python -m unittest discover

$ cd [location of multicast_chat]
$ python -m unittest discover

By modifying python path:

> set PYTHONPATH=[location of multicast_chat parent]
> python -m unittest discover -s [location of multicast_chat parent]

$ PYTHONPATH=[location of multicast_chat parent] \
    python -m unittest discover -s [location of multicast_chat parent]

Your own project in different location:

> set PYTHONPATH=[location of my_multicast_chat parent];[location of network-course]
> python -m unittest discover -s [location of multicast_chat parent]

$ PYTHONPATH=[location of my_multicast_chat parent];[location of network-course] \
    python -m unittest discover -s [location of my_multicast_chat parent]

FORMAT CHECK EXECUTION
----------------------

> python -m pyflakes *.py
> python -m pep8 *.py

$ pyflakes *.py
$ pep8 *.py
